{"tid":151283,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"玩開日本玩具的巴絲，有幾多係唔搵鋪頭，直接自己係官網訂?","createTime":"2017-03-10T17:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T01:46:37.000Z","uid":29696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee519fcf74ff8a39f78cdf960e3efd18e9bb87d9","tid":151283,"uid":29696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"我個人比較經常係官網海外store / amiami / amazon訂<br />\n直接快捷唔怕cut單，當然個網唔會西你面<br />\n<br />\n但直接食匯價，同硬食運費(得自己一個訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"5ce4a47498b0f79e8fa2b48c206c842cc51a532f","tid":151283,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:28:46.000Z","msg":"唔敢入鋪頭訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b70a9d2aa21e006a8da70ea5f2f006e33badf3","tid":151283,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"係網訂有得扣稅<br />\n果度都減左一半運費<br />\n匯率果一萬幾千yan差得唔係幾多<br />\n到貨又準時又唔會有爭議<br />\n例如cut單臨時加價果d<br />\n而且送埋上門唔洗係間舖搬返屋企<br />\n見到個日文紙皮箱同埋隻野係日版無個行價label<br />\n精神上都開心d自我感覺良好<br />\n試過網訂真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5445ed42f5ce3b438b6d9e94cefad1e9105ff7","tid":151283,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"淨係運費嗰幾百都等如食左炒價啦"},{"pid":"15be181e3ef68d9483b750865900c416bfee3e3c","tid":151283,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係運費嗰幾百都等如食左炒價啦</blockquote><br />\n正常土人運費幾十蚊<br />\n大盒既figure上次先運左百幾二百蚊<br />\n減稅盒野平左大約一百<br />\n計返個價同係香港買一樣<br />\n仲要有人送到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3e5c1275774fe110555ce7eae0ccfbc6041d4d","tid":151283,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係運費嗰幾百都等如食左炒價啦</blockquote><br />\n正常土人運費幾十蚊<br />\n大盒既figure上次先運左百幾二百蚊<br />\n減稅盒野平左大約一百<br />\n計返個價同係香港買一樣<br />\n仲要有人送到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以介紹下有咩網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d74390ded7532928be000c53eba5a3151d2b85b","tid":151283,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係運費嗰幾百都等如食左炒價啦</blockquote><br />\n就算一樣價錢都唔撚比班炒狗賺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bc83419067dcfcfd433748f796f6a3dfecd597","tid":151283,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:22:41.000Z","msg":"網購真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比多少少就可以安坐家中等貨到<br />\n唔洗出去左搵右搵受舖頭氣，d時間車錢成本都係返曬度<br />\n<br />\n一試就上曬癮買到就破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd509345ce229fe052bca8e2ecdbe29014e49e6f","tid":151283,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係運費嗰幾百都等如食左炒價啦</blockquote><br />\n我寧願比運費都撚益炒貨狗啦"},{"pid":"3d9604cb76f3801140a8a1928a9106796ead9704","tid":151283,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打同我一樣 <br />\n<br />\n一定要出舖頭買 ，因為有得check qc ，唔岩就換"},{"pid":"30f4decb9fcf56d0c2e99dd078070dae09d94867","tid":151283,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:30:21.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"a1aa7737318d7866d13848fd59ab6fbabc250df2","tid":151283,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"網上訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢事同人迫"},{"pid":"1c79b22d982b149039522e452f103e480b575932","tid":151283,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc